jLTMOnYZzySghRX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113913nqMDwRld2PAhgC7I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113913rh4NoOZWH0AQGTMK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113914xJZNjpsd8cGR27Ol.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113915o8yBwuEkcnj3aV0i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113915vNWu8C1XKljzGgbF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113916ueTxGhVdZ5pE9Uyt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113917FAjWuyNJawKz1Dm3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811271139175PBrduxHpwmSRVyb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113918lmcfZDkyO06MrPdz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113919Ff2gRu64DQviHUm9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113919x0SlpyVnr21RCtcN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113920YieKT5v7Jgh48jUH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811271139205yHXZLU6FP8Dhl27.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113921dNklJTcZwUKDYy5h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113921djs5LZt7E1qM8hAX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127113922v02y8O5WUxD6kBpM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/2019-pre-fall/new-york/roberto-cavalli/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Roberto Cavalli 发布 2019 早秋成衣系列：</a></strong></p><p>创意总监 Paul Surridge 上任刚过一年。他在展示新系列时特别提出品牌反映当下文化环境变化的重要性：“Cavalli 一直是个非常女性的品牌，但女性的定义已经和传统中追随的雍容华贵不一样了。它是一个全球性的生意，我需要让它变得更容易接近，一切法则和价值都需要做调整。”</p><p>因此在这个系列里，你会看到朋克感的纹身上衣和连衣裙，但因为剪裁和半透明材质，它并不显得过于性感或叛逆，而是更加温和优雅；也会看到本季十分流行、也是 Cavalli 特有的动物花纹，出现在更多不同风格的单品上：夹克、半裙、风衣、皮草外套。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114958iCtE9qQ6covSnfbG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115013Yo5mQVPs0ZBzeUcq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114950yzAvB60KEi9tMbId.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114949tFS6Hjkh8yvGA40I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114943CQGN3vBfJIRk0bhe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114950J3bP2aW4FpXyDGCw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.344070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114951BfuxUKHIs5EjQmgp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114952CqlvBickW9RINmJY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114952TakxpHRSZGBLczN7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114953JPYCUVX0k3KMt8Wb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114954KZC3qnzrxDNloFUy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.344070\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114954PDc6AVt2dBuzLjYg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114955V9f3BjC7DiWMoXLZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114956lpe05unJLcQxPFA4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114957oxI1iLqfmpgHPO8Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114957KkbC7DJBPIFNvESA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.489019\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018112711495826YUK9R3oWkerjf5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127114959IAt02LQHGzTloKqX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115000cIZvesA43FDh0GKY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115000IyDmEYHhW5PqZVUi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115001zhuTp61b9LsyweqH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811271150071WuGnCaRAFso9fN2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.392387\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811271150079kjb8KJrovgmxIUq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115008E3sThzmdy0WpkY25.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811271150096gVLwDEWJq9yj831.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115011uVQ9hn6eiwfdEm8l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115011sSW45L6m8PG7fiVX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115012n1zWAUPv2JZq8QyB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115014HWFP4upyLQXgoCic.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115015fubWw6vtjFCB5iLn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127115015wVMJm258GpDKzF4P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498047\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>墨尔本时尚设计师 Betty Liu 想通过自己的作品探讨西方在对东方的注视中，如何将旗袍变成了物化女性身体的工具，并且通过弱化性别特质的设计，审视这种对亚洲典型形象的偏见。</p><p>在新系列中，她让模特们穿上宽大的旗袍与饭桌上的食物互动，通过把典型元素放大、和常见场景里不常见的互动，制造出一种具有讽刺意味的美感。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/betty-liu-jess-brohier-eating-the-other-work-fashion-261118\" rel=\"nofollow\">摄影师 Jess Brohier 把现场记录了下来，并取名为&nbsp;<em>Eating the Other。</em></a></strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130540AuwT8ylr5EQfLkMI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130531cpa6RVlUKNZSr5zW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130652V0OUwMLhCpDN2FlY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130644jemTzuqCE7s1bdtX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130539LQxgJnD27c6loOh4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.486188\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130511CNB9jI7vWYbfuEQ6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130514J1cLIDZswy4la3r2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130520JaptEVecX1hiLrIF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130535qxKLGE3e7CUNOAmf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811271305323PgLpEkvHUCyA2Yl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130536EiSD80VO5TvLJQYs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130537wxZpoN9gjUs0I1QP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130704Q5motVO9IfgJPRcl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130539jt729UFAmrqBGKxa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130536JXCMF1QYhjlrawNt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181127130537DoCSUQrgBfpXe6lq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为 <a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/betty-liu-jess-brohier-eating-the-other-work-fashion-261118\" rel=\"nofollow\">Betty Liu 设计作品、Jess Brohier&nbsp;摄影</a><br></p>"}